column1: # This file defines some mappings for the newbase parameters. Notice that when parameters
# are searched with incomplete information (i.e. levelId
# etc. missing) then parameters are tested in the same order as they appear in this file.
# The "mapping_newbase_auto.csv"  file contains mappings that cannot be found from this
# file. You might want to move some of those mappings to this file in order to define
#            11 Level at specified pressure difference from ground to level
#            13 Layer between two metric heights above ground
#            14 Layer between two depths below land surface
#         bit 0 = Climatological parameter (=> ignore year when searching)
# 11) Search match (Can this mapping used when searching mappings for incomplete parameters)
# 12) Mapping function (enables data conversions during the mapping)
